name: gcc_impl_linux-aarch64
raw_recipe:
# This file created by conda-build 3.21.8
# ------------------------------------------------

package:
  name: gcc_impl_linux-aarch64
  version: 11.2.0
source:
  - patches:
      - patches/0021-Hardcode-HAVE_ALIGNED_ALLOC-1-in-libstdc-v3-configur.patch
      - patches/old-allow-commands-in-main-specfile.patch
    sha256: f0837f1bf8244a5cc23bd96ff6366712a791cfae01df8e25b137698aca26efc1
    url: https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gcc/gcc-11.2.0/gcc-11.2.0.tar.gz
build:
  detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
  ignore_run_exports:
    - __glibc
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*'
  number: 16
  runpath_whitelist:
    - x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libpthread-2.12.2.so
  string: h4d2f25f_16
requirements:
  build:
    - binutils_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1 he24a65f_2
    - gcc_bootstrap_linux-64 11.2.0 h6cd0796_9
    - gfortran_impl_linux-aarch64 11.2.0.*
    - gxx_impl_linux-aarch64 11.2.0.*
    - kernel-headers_linux-aarch64 4.18.0 h5b4a56d_13
    - ld_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1 h4e2ea54_2
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17 h43d7e78_13
  host:
    - kernel-headers_linux-aarch64 4.18.0 h5b4a56d_13
    - libgcc-ng 11.2.0 hf1cc4e7_16
    - libgfortran5 >=11.2.0,<12.0a0
    - libgomp 11.2.0 hf1cc4e7_16
    - libsanitizer 11.2.0 h0d0a5bb_16
    - libstdcxx-ng 11.2.0 h0d0a5bb_16
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17 h43d7e78_13
  run:
    - binutils_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1.*
    - libgcc-devel_linux-aarch64 11.2.0 hb955bc9_16
    - libgcc-ng >=11.2.0
    - libgomp >=11.2.0
    - libsanitizer 11.2.0 h0d0a5bb_16
    - libstdcxx-ng >=11.2.0
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64
test:
  commands:
    - echo conda_cos7
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgomp.so
    - test `readlink ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgomp.so` == "../../lib/libgomp.so"
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda_cos7-linux-gnu-gcc
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda_cos7-linux-gnu-cpp
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-gcc
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-cpp
    - test ! -f ${PREFIX}/bin/gcc
    - test ! -f ${PREFIX}/bin/cpp
    - CC=$(${PREFIX}/bin/*-gcc -dumpmachine)-gcc
    - ${CC} -Wall tests/aligned_alloc.c -c -o c_aligned.o -v -fsanitize=address
    - ${CC} -Wall tests/aligned_alloc.c -c -o c_aligned.o -v
    - ${CC} -Wall c_aligned.o -o c_aligned -v && ./c_aligned
    - ${CC} -Wall c_aligned.o -o c_aligned -Wl,-rpath,/foo && aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-readelf
      -d c_aligned | grep RPATH | grep "/foo:${PREFIX}/lib"
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgcc_s.so
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgomp.spec
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libsanitizer.spec
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libasan_preinit.o
  files:
    - tests
  requires:
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17.*
about:
  home: https://gcc.gnu.org/
  license: GPL-3.0-only WITH GCC-exception-3.1
  summary: GNU C Compiler
extra:
  copy_test_source_files: true
  final: true
  recipe-maintainers:
    - beckermr
    - isuruf
    - timsnyder
    - xhochy

commands: ${CC} -Wall c_aligned.o -o c_aligned -Wl,-rpath,/foo && aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-readelf -d c_aligned | grep RPATH | grep "/foo:${PREFIX}/lib"
